here , i would like to explain the consideration of the cpc central committee on the major issue and key measure mention in the decision of the third plenary session of the 18th cpc central committee .
first , allow the market to play the decisive role in allocate resource and let the government perform its function better .
this be a major theoretical proposition in the decision , because the reform of the economic system be still the focus of continue the reform comprehensively , and the appropriate handling of the relationship between the government and the market be still the core issue of the reform of the economic system .
in 1992 the party ’s 14th national congress stipulate that china ’s economic reform aim at establish a socialist market economy , allow the market to play a basic role in allocate resource under state macro control .
this key breakthrough in theory play a extremely important role in guide china ’s reform and opening-up effort , and its economic and social development .
it also illustrate that theoretical innovation pave the way for innovation in practice .
