it be emphasize in the decision that we must unswervingly consolidate and develop the public economy , persist in the lead role of public ownership , give full play to the lead role of the state-owned economy , and incessantly increase its vitality , leverage power and impact .
adhere to and further the relevant deliberation make since the party ’s 15th national congress , the decision propose to vigorously develop the mixed-ownership economy .
it stress that such a economy , with cross-shareholding by and integration of state-owned capital , collective capital and non-public capital , be important to materialize the basic economic system of china .
it will help to improve the function of state-owned capital , maintain and increase its value and raise its competitiveness .
it be a effective channel and inevitable choice for we to adhere to the lead role of public ownership and improve the vitality , leverage power and impact of the state-owned economy in the new condition .
the decision state that china will improve the state asset management system , strengthen state asset oversight with capital management at the core , and reform the authorize operation mechanism for state capital .
state-owned capital investment operation must serve the strategic goal of the state , invest more in key industry and area that be vital to national security and be the lifeblood of the economy , focus on offer public service , develop important and future-oriented strategic industry , protect the ecological environment , support scientific and technological progress , and guarantee national security .
the government will transfer part of the state-owned capital to social security fund .
we will increase the proportion of state-owned capital gain that be turn over to the public finance , to be use to ensure and improve the people ’s livelihood .
state-owned enterprise ( so ) constitute a important force for advance modernization and protect the common interest of the people .
