the decision propose a series of target reform measure : we must ensure that state-owned capital increase its input into public-service-oriented enterprise ; in natural monopoly industry in which state-owned capital continue to hold control interest , carry out a reform focus on separation of government administration from enterprise management , separation of government administration from state asset management , franchise operation , and government oversight , separate network ownership from operation , and deregulate control over competitive business in light of the condition of different industry ; improve the corporate governance structure to ensure smooth operation and effective check and balance ; establish a system of professional manager , and give better play to the role of business executive ; establish a long-term incentive-and-restraint mechanism , and strengthen investigation into the accountability of soe operation and investment ; and explore way to publicize important information , include soe financial budget .
