reform of the fiscal and taxation system be one of the key point in continue the reform comprehensively .
the reform mainly include improvement of the budgeting and taxation system , and establishment of a system in which authority of office match responsibility for expenditure .
the decision stipulate that we will adopt a complete , standardized , open and transparent budget system , and appropriately increase the authority of office and responsibility of expenditure of the central government , include those concern national defense , foreign affair , national security , and unified national market rule and management .
the authority of office over some social security program , and the construction and maintenance of major trans-regional project will be share by the central and local government , and the authority of office will be gradually clarify in this regard .
the central government can delegate some expenditure responsibility to local government through transfer payment .
in term of trans-regional public service with great impact on other region , the central government will shoulder some of the expenditure responsibility of local government through transfer payment .
the main aim of the reform be to clearly define authority of office , reform the taxation system , make tax burden stable and budget transparent , and increase efficiency .
it also aim to accelerate the development of a modern fiscal system that be conducive to the transformation of the economic growth pattern , the establishment of a fair market under unified rule , and the promotion of equal access to basic public service ; develop fiscal and taxation system that be compatible with the financial resource and authority of office of the central and local government ; and mobilize the initiative of both the central and local government .
reform of the fiscal and taxation system be a step-by-step process , and will take some time to complete .
the party central committee have clearly state that we must maintain the stability of the current financial pattern of the central and local government , and further rationalize the division of revenue between they .
fourth , improve mechanism and institution for the integrate development of urban and rural area .
the unbalanced development between urban and rural area be a serious problem hinder the development of we economy and society , a major problem we must solve in order to complete the building of a moderately prosperous society in all respects and accelerate socialist modernization .
