the decision propose reform measure to improve the mechanism and institution for the integrate development of urban and rural area : one , accelerate the building of a new type of agricultural operation system .
we will maintain the fundamental status of family operation in agriculture ; encourage the transfer of contract land-use right to big , specialized operator , family farm , farmer ’ cooperative and agrobusiness ; encourage rural area to develop cooperative economy ; encourage and guide industrial and commercial capital to invest in rural area to develop modern planting and breed industry suit to commercialized management ; and allow farmer to develop industrialized operation of agriculture by become shareholder use they contract land-use right , among other measure .
two , endow farmer with more property rights .
we will protect farmer ’ contract land-use right by law , safeguard the rights and interest of farmer as member of collective economic organization , ensure rural household ’ usufruct of they homestead , and select several pilot area to steadily and prudently push forward the mortgage , guarantee and transfer of farmer ’ residential property rights .
three , promote equal exchange of factor of production and balanced allocation of public resource between urban and rural area .
we will ensure migrant worker receive equal pay for equal work , and ensure farmer equally share the gain from add value of land ; improve the agricultural insurance system ; encourage investment in rural development , and permit enterprise and social organization to start all kind of undertaking in rural area ; make a balanced allocation of compulsory education resource between urban and rural area , integrate the basic old-age insurance and health-care insurance system of urban and rural resident , and improve the balanced development of the minimum living allowance system in both urban and rural area ; and steadily make basic urban public service available to all permanent resident in city , and incorporate farmer who have settle down in urban area into the urban housing and social security network .
fifth , promote wide , multi-tiered and institutionalized consultative democracy .
consultative democracy be a unique form and distinctive advantage of china ’s socialist democracy , and a important embodiment of the party ’s mass line in the political field .
promote consultative democracy be conducive to improve the people ’s orderly participation in political affair , strengthen the tie between the party and the people , and promote scientific and democratic decision-making .
