the decision stress that , under the leadership of the party , china will promote consultation throughout society with regard to major issue of economic and social development , and practical issue closely related to the interest of the people , and adhere to the principle of consultation before policy-making and during policy implementation .
we will build a consultative democracy feature appropriate procedure and complete segment to expand the consultation channel cover organ of state power , committee of the chinese people ’s political consultative conference ( cppcc ) , political party , and community-level and social organization ; conduct intensive consultation on issue relate to legislation , administration , democracy , political participation and social problem ; give full play to the important role of the unite front in consultative democracy , make the cppcc serve as a major channel for conduct consultative democracy , improve the system of the cppcc , specify the contents and procedure for consultation , diversify form of consultative democracy , and more actively carry out orderly consultation on particular issue with those work on these issue , with representative from all sector of society , and with the relevant government department on the handling of proposal , and increase the frequency of consultation to improve they effectiveness .
