we be now mainly challenge by the follow problem : anti-corruption force perform function separately make it difficult to build up synergy ; some case be not deal with resolutely ; and the accountability system be too lax to handle reoccur corruption case .
the decision lay out plan for promote innovation in the anti-corruption mechanism and institution , and strengthen institutional guarantee .
the main point be : strengthen the party ’s unified leadership to build a clean and honest government and combat corruption ; ensure that party committee bear primary responsibility and the commission for discipline inspection take the responsibility for oversight , and work out and implement a feasible accountability system ; improve the lead and work mechanism for anti-corruption effort , reform and improve the function of anti-corruption coordination group at all level , and leave the investigation of corruption case mainly to commission for discipline inspection of higher level ; strengthen the leadership role of the higher level over the lower level of the discipline inspection commission , and the simultaneous reporting of the related investigation process to the party committee at the same level and the commission for discipline inspection at the next-higher level ; and fully ensure that the central commission for discipline inspection dispatch resident discipline inspection agency to the central-level department of the party and the government , and improve the discipline inspection system at both the central and local level , so that it cover all region , all sector , all enterprise and all public institution .
