the guide thought be : ensure people ’s property rights to natural resource accord to the principle of separation between ownership and management , one issue belong to one department , and establish a unify responsibility mechanism for people who act on behalf of the public to manage public natural resource asset .
there be a difference between the state ’s exercise of power and management over the natural resource asset own by the whole people and the state ’s supervision and management of the natural resource within its territory .
