this require we to improve the system of oversight of natural resource , and fulfill we duty as the manager of we territorial space .
the owner of state-owned natural resource asset and the manager of state natural resource must act independently , while cooperate with and supervise each other .
we need to realize that we mountain , water , forest , farmland and lake form a living community .
the lifeline of the people come from the farmland , that of the farmland come from the water , that of the water come from the mountain , that of the mountain come from the earth , and that of the earth come from the tree .
to control the exploitation of natural resource and restore the ecosystem , we must follow the law of nature .
if people only tend to they own responsibility , for example , grow tree , regulate river or protect farmland in isolation , they be prone to gain in one area and lose in another , which eventually lead to systemic destruction of the ecology .
therefore , it be of the utmost importance to put one department in charge of the usage of the entire territory of a country , and carry out unify protection and restoration program for its natural resource .
eleventh , establish the lead group for continue the reform comprehensively under the cpc central committee .
